// wt_crawler.cpp
// Single-file Wt application that provides a UI for the crawler + integrated search.
// Combines a lightweight crawler (based on provided crawler code), SQLite storage (with FTS5),
// and a Wt UI with Dashboard, Frontier, Detail and Search screens.
//
// Build (example):
// g++ wt_crawler.cpp -o wt_crawler -std=c++17 `pkg-config --cflags --libs wt` -lcurl -lsqlite3 -lxml2 -lcrypto -pthread
//
// Run:
// ./wt_crawler --docroot . --http-address 0.0.0.0 --http-port 8080
//
// Notes:
// - This is an amalgamated single-file example intended as a working skeleton.
// - It implements core DB schema, a background worker loop, simple fetch+parse, and Wt UI + REST resources.
// - For production use, harden error handling, sanitize inputs, and respect robots.txt / legal constraints.

